*.log

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Files we WANT to commit (override the above if needed):
#   model/saved/dosha_model.pt   ← trained model (~1.7 MB)
#   model/saved/rf_baseline.pkl  ← RF baseline
#   dataset/data.json            ← feature metadata (no images)
#   frontend/*                   ← served as static files
